Real-Time Processing: Instant user profile updates with event streaming
LLM Integration: Seamless content personalization using language models
A/B Testing: Segment-aware experimentation framework
Security: JWT auth, encryption, rate limiting, RBAC
Fault Tolerance: Circuit breakers, retry mechanisms, graceful degradation
Scalability: Async processing, caching, concurrent execution
Monitoring: Health metrics, performance tracking, adaptive logging